			<div class="content" id="post-content-3726750">
									

<p>Okay, I've finally worked up the courage to post this, let's see how it plays out. Writing an -EX has been a goal of mine since I started contributing to the site, and this is the closest I could get &#8212; it may not be <em>technically</em> explained, but it's still valid in-universe. I also wanted to write something that was literally just a monster, and a large, carnivorous, nocturnal mammal fit the bill nicely.</p>
<p>The whole thing was inspired by me walking my dog on a field at night, and realising I could only see her through the corner of my eye &#8212; <a href="http://lacrossetribune.com/tomahjournal/entertainment/peripheral-vision-offers-better-night-sight/article_b9c2363e-7fb8-5656-b7de-bb6c4b63cd68.html">this article explains the phenomenon pretty well</a>. In any case, I hope you enjoy my scip about an invisible creature that may or may not exist.</p>
